Package net.sourceforge.plantuml.descdiagram

package net.sourceforge.plantuml.descdiagram
Provides classes used to manage PlantUML Description Diagram.

The PlantUML Description Diagrams are:

  • Use Case Diagram;
  • Component Diagram;
  • Deployment Diagram;
  • Archimate Diagram;
  • Problem Diagram;
  • Object Diagram.
